1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if your body sent messages that could start a storm?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:09,200
Cytokines are like text messages for immune cells, guiding responses to infections.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,400
But what happens when those messages go haywire?

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:18,000
In a cytokine storm, excessive signals can overwhelm the body, leading to severe inflammation.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,800
This dysregulation may contribute to conditions like COVID-19, but research is ongoing.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,200
Want to understand your immunity better?

7
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,200
Follow for more science insights!
